body:
Comment 6: 
Here are the ones which remain:

The 10 which pipe into "cmp -D $D/$F.out" are already handled by test/run.go, but since
the magic shell strings are no longer recognized (now that we're using testlib), they're
back to being skipped.

I'll look at adding cmp support to testlib for now.
